div.div:
1) server starts sending questions to all the connected streams
2) starts the timer & waits for inputs
3) matches the input
4) if matches, increments score
5) else waits for all to finish
6) if the timer ends/all players answer correctly, send next question
7) if the target score reaches to any one player, declare result & exit
8) if all players leave, target time reached exit
